WE ARE TALKING ABOUT DE;IVERY 

1 COURIES SERVER

INSTALL USING
$ sudo apt install courier-pop -y

THEN
$ sudo apt install courier-imap

NOW GO TO
$ sudo nano /etc/courier/authdaemonrc

FOR POP3 CONFIG FILE IS LOCATED AT
/etc/courier/pop3d

TO CHANGE PATH OF FILE EDIT IT AND INSERT THE RUOT

AND SAME FOR IMAP 
$ sudo nano /etc/courier/imapd

NOW RESTART THE SERVICE
$ sudo service courier-pop restart
$ sdup service courier-imap restart

[2] deovecto server

INSTALL
$ sudo apt install dovecot-imapd dovecote-pop3d -y

NAVIGATE TO FIND CONFIGURATION FILE
/etc/dovecot/conf.d
or 
/etc/dovecot/dovecote.conf

ACTUALLY WE SHOULD USE THIS COMMAND NAME
$ dovecot -n 		# shows dovecot configuration
